## android/gradle.properties:
```
APP_UPLOAD_STORE_FILE=upload-key.keystore         # Path to the "keystore" file
APP_UPLOAD_KEY_ALIAS=miApp-key                # Replace with value of the `keystore.keyAlias` field in the credentials.json file
APP_UPLOAD_STORE_PASSWORD=p.assword#123         # Replace with value of the `keystore.password` field in the credentials.json file
APP_UPLOAD_KEY_PASSWORD=p.assword#123           # Replace with value of the `keystore.keyPassword` field in the credentials.json file
```

## android/app/build.gradle:

```
signingConfigs {
    release {
        if (project.hasProperty('APP_UPLOAD_STORE_FILE')) {
            storeFile file(APP_UPLOAD_STORE_FILE)
            storePassword APP_UPLOAD_STORE_PASSWORD
            keyAlias APP_UPLOAD_KEY_ALIAS
            keyPassword APP_UPLOAD_KEY_PASSWORD
        }
    }
}


buildTypes {
    release {
        signingConfig signingConfigs.release
        ...
    }
}
```

## Build Release APK
`cd android`
`./gradlew app:bundleRelease`